<p>
Double-click the menu bar.
</p></td></tr>
<tr><td valign=top align=center>
<table width=1 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 align=left class=screenshotmarginleft><tr><td align=left><img class=screenshot width=640 height=480 src='pics/tutorials/windows311forworkgroups/23.png'></td></tr></table>
</td><td valign=top style='padding-bottom: 3em;'>
<p>
Double-click the Main group icon.
</p></td></tr>
<tr><td valign=top align=center>
<table width=1 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 align=left class=screenshotmarginleft><tr><td align=left><img class=screenshot width=640 height=480 src='pics/tutorials/windows311forworkgroups/24.png'></td></tr></table>
</td><td valign=top style='padding-bottom: 3em;'>
<p>
Double-click the Accessories group icon.
</p></td></tr>
<tr><td valign=top align=center>
<table width=1 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 align=left class=screenshotmarginleft><tr><td align=left><img class=screenshot width=640 height=480 src='pics/tutorials/windows311forworkgroups/25.png'></td></tr></table>
</td><td valign=top style='padding-bottom: 3em;'>
<p>
You can use your mouse to drag an item from one area of the screen
to another.
</p><p>
Click the mouse button to continue.
</p></td></tr>
<tr><td valign=top align=center>
<table width=1 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 align=left class=screenshotmarginleft><tr><td align=left><img class=screenshot width=640 height=480 src='pics/tutorials/windows311forworkgroups/26.png'></td></tr></table>
</td><td valign=top style='padding-bottom: 3em;'>
<p>
Drag each item on your screen to its correct location in the window:
<ol>
<li>Move the pointer to the item you want to drag.
<li>Press and hold down the mouse button.
<li>Move the item to the new location.
<li>Release the mouse button to drop the item in its new location.
</ol>
</p><p>
Drag the Control-menu box to its window location.
</p></td></tr>
<tr><td valign=top align=center>
<table width=1 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 align=left class=screenshotmarginleft><tr><td align=left><img class=screenshot width=640 height=480 src='pics/tutorials/windows311forworkgroups/27.png'></td></tr></table>
</td><td valign=top style='padding-bottom: 3em;'>
<p>
Drag the title bar to its window location.
</p></td></tr>
